token_lists.title: Photography
token_lists.description: I have been a photography enthusiast before I started to collect digital art, so I think it is fitting to have a board with my favourite photography on Versum.

token_lists.title: La Mer
token_lists.description: Pieces of sea, captured in an infinite movement, becomes an elusive moving object, an optical illusion made of thousands of particles, grouped in crests or dispersed in troughs such as a marine snow.

token_lists.title: Unwanted memories
token_lists.description:
Recently I found in closet couple of drawings I saved from my art therapy sessions 15 years ago. Not ready to share originals (yet?), so I'm starting this series of works with MidJourney
